TextMagicResponseParser
public class TextMagicJSONResponseParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements TextMagicResponseParser

The default TextMagicResponseParser implementation. Parses JSON-based http api responses.
The implementation use "org.json" library for JSON parsing

Author:
Rafael Bagmanov
